<div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);padding:1.5rem;border-radius:1rem"><h3>Processar pedidos</h3><p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);font-size:0.875rem;margin-top:0.5rem">Para gerenciar suas compras e envios</p></div>
<div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);padding:1.5rem;border-radius:1rem"><h3>Pagamentos seguros</h3><p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);font-size:0.875rem;margin-top:0.5rem">Processar transações de forma segura</p></div>
<div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);padding:1.5rem;border-radius:1rem"><h3>Prevenção de fraude</h3><p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);font-size:0.875rem;margin-top:0.5rem">Detectar atividades suspeitas</p></div>
<div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);padding:1.5rem;border-radius:1rem"><h3>Melhorar serviços</h3><p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);font-size:0.875rem;margin-top:0.5rem">Personalizar sua experiência</p></div></div>
<h2 style="color:#D4FF00;font-size:1.5rem;margin:2rem 0 1rem">Seus direitos</h2>
<div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));gap:1rem;margin-bottom:2rem">
<div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);padding:1.5rem;border-radius:1rem"><h3 style="color:#D4FF00;margin-bottom:0.5rem">Acesso</h3><p style="font-size:0.875rem">Solicitar cópia dos seus dados</p></div>
<div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);padding:1.5rem;border-radius:1rem"><h3 style="color:#D4FF00;margin-bottom:0.5rem">Retificação</h3><p style="font-size:0.875rem">Atualizar informações incorretas</p></div>
<div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);padding:1.5rem;border-radius:1rem"><h3 style="color:#D4FF00;margin-bottom:0.5rem">Eliminação</h3><p style="font-size:0.875rem">Solicitar eliminação de dados</p></div>
<div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);padding:1.5rem;border-radius:1rem"><h3 style="color:#D4FF00;margin-bottom:0.5rem">Portabilidade</h3><p style="font-size:0.875rem">Receber dados em formato legível</p></div></div>
<div style="background:rgba(212,255,0,0.1);border:2px solid rgba(212,255,0,0.3);border-radius:1rem;padding:2rem;text-align:center">
<h3 style="font-size:1.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem">Dúvidas sobre privacidade?</h3>
